<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM3.7.5">
<l>tāyeṉai yeṉṟiraṅkāḷ taṭantōḷita ṉakkamainta</l>
<l>māyaṉai mātavaṉai matitteṉṉaiya kaṉṟavivaḷ</l>
<l>vēyaṉa tōḷviciṟip peṭaiyaṉṉame ṉanaṭantu</l>
<l>pōyiṉa pūṅkoṭiyāḷ puṉalālipu kuvarkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She does not pity [me], calling me ‘mother.’ The girl with shapely arms,</l>
<l>She who left me, thinking [only] of Mādhava,</l>
<l rend="indent">of Māyaṉ who is perfect for her,</l>
<l>The one [like] a blossoming liana who departed [as she] walks like a hen swan,</l>
<l>Swinging her bamboo-like arms, are they setting out for Āli</l>
<l rend="indent">with profuse waters?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
